{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 74,
    "name": "سُورَةُ المُدَّثِّرِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Muddaththir",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Cloaked One",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 56,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 5496,
        "text": "盖被的人啊！",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5497,
        "text": "你应当起来，你应当警告，",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5498,
        "text": "你应当颂扬你的主宰，",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5499,
        "text": "你应当洗涤你的衣服，",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5500,
        "text": "你应当远离污秽，",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5501,
        "text": "你不要施恩而求厚报，",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5502,
        "text": "你应当为你的主而坚忍。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5503,
        "text": "当号角被吹向的时候，",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5504,
        "text": "在那时，将有一个艰难的日子。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5505,
        "text": "那个日子对不信道的人们，是不容易渡过的。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5506,
        "text": "你让我独自处治我所创造的那个人吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5507,
        "text": "我赏赐他丰富的财产，",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5508,
        "text": "和在跟前的子嗣，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5509,
        "text": "我提高了他的声望，",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5510,
        "text": "而他还冀望我再多加赏赐。",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5511,
        "text": "绝不然，他确实是反对我的迹象的，",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5512,
        "text": "我将使他遭受苦难。",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5513,
        "text": "他碓已思考，确已计划。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5514,
        "text": "但无论他怎样计划，他是被弃绝的。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5515,
        "text": "无论他怎样计划，他终是被弃绝的。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5516,
        "text": "他看一看，",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5517,
        "text": "然后皱眉蹙额，",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5518,
        "text": "然后高傲地转过身去，",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5519,
        "text": "而且说：这只是传习的魔术，",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5520,
        "text": "这只是凡人的言辞。",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5521,
        "text": "我将使他堕入火狱，",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5522,
        "text": "你怎能知道火狱是什么？",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5523,
        "text": "它不让任何物存在，不许任何物留下，",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5524,
        "text": "它烧灼肌肤。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5525,
        "text": "管理它的，共计十九名。",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5526,
        "text": "我只将管理火狱的成天神，我只以他们的数目，考验不信道的人们，以便曾受天经的人们认清，而信道的人们更加笃信；以免曾受天经的人们和信道的人们怀疑；以便心中有病者和不信道者说：真主设这个譬喻做什么？真主这样使他所意欲的人误入迷途，使他所意欲的人遵循正路。只有你的主，能知道他的军队，这只是人类的教训。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5527,
        "text": "真的，以月亮盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5528,
        "text": "以逝去的黑夜盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5529,
        "text": "以显照的黎明盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5530,
        "text": "火狱确是一个大难，",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5531,
        "text": "可以警告人类，",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5532,
        "text": "警告你们中欲前进者或欲后退者；",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5533,
        "text": "各人将因自己的营谋而作抵押，",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5534,
        "text": "惟幸福的人们除外。",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5535,
        "text": "他们在乐园中互相询问，",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5536,
        "text": "问犯罪人们的情状，",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5537,
        "text": "你们为什么堕入火狱呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5538,
        "text": "他们说：我们没有礼拜，",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5539,
        "text": "也没有济贫，",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5540,
        "text": "我们与妄言的人们一道妄言，",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5541,
        "text": "我们否认报应日，",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5542,
        "text": "一直到死亡降临了我们。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5543,
        "text": "说情者的说情，将无益於他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5544,
        "text": "他们怎么退避这教训呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5545,
        "text": "他们好像一群惊慌的驴子，",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5546,
        "text": "刚逃避了一只狮子一样。",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5547,
        "text": "不然，他们中的每个人都希望获得一些展开的天经。",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5548,
        "text": "绝不然，他们不畏惧后世！",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5549,
        "text": "真的，这《古兰经》确是一个教诲！",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5550,
        "text": "谁愿意，谁记忆它，",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5551,
        "text": "他们只因真主的意欲而记忆它。他是应受敬畏的，他是宜於赦宥的。",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
      "identifier": "zh.jian",
